{"word":"εἰσδέχομαι","slug":"εἰσδέχομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>εἰσδέχομαι</b></el> <el>(ionic <el>ἐς-δέκομαι</el>) (<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-δέξομαι</el>) </el><p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a>:— <i>to take into, admit</i>, <el>ἐς τὸ ἱρόν</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>; <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <el>ἄντροις εἰσδέξασθαί τινα</el> <i>to receive</i> him <i>in</i> the cave, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>; <el>εἰσδ. τινα ὑπόστεγον</el> <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/>"}]}